snippet.title: [UPDATED 1] Super Mario New Star RELEASE Trailer - Download In Description [EN/FR]
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD HERE

Super Mario New Star is a SM64 Major Hack (132 stars)
by Midoji / Sanji02 (me) (it's my first hack)

2012-2014


French Version (par Moi, corrigée par Korambu) :

https://www.mediafire.com/?kg85xf278kakbr7

English Version (by ChocoPain, corrigée par Crash) :

https://www.mediafire.com/?wpic734p6x8b2pn

Unfortunately a bug persists in the world 10 (the background) :/

Bugs Fixed :

- The Big boo's star of world 2 is accessible.
- "Got A Star" theme is restored
- More text
- Mr.Eye's star 
- the Koopa Freeze
